## Deadline Management Workflow

- [ ] 1. Capture all deadlines: List every deliverable and its due date
- [ ] 2. Assess risk: Which deadlines are at risk based on current progress?
- [ ] 3. Prioritize: Focus on at-risk items first
- [ ] 4. Follow up: Proactively check status with owners
- [ ] 5. Escalate: Flag at-risk deadlines to stakeholders early
- [ ] 6. Adjust: Help find solutions when deadlines are at risk
- [ ] 7. Confirm delivery: Track actual vs. committed delivery dates

## Key Inputs
- Project: {{project_name}}
- All deadlines: {{deadlines}}
- Current progress: {{current_progress}}
- At-risk items: {{at_risk_items}}
